## 8. Compliance, Monitoring & Enforcement
The exceptions log is reviewed at each Steering Committee meeting and at management review. Operating outside policy without an approved exception is a policy violation handled per `../people/hr-security-policy.md.template`. Expired exceptions that are still being relied upon are treated as findings in the POA&M register (`corrective-action-poam.md.template`).

